# Google Maps Platform API key, used for real address autocomplete (Places API)
# when creating/editing a Reinigungsobjekt (Standort) in Montora.
#
# How to get one:
#   1. https://console.cloud.google.com/google/maps-apis/credentials
#   2. Create (or select) a project, then create an API key.
#   3. Enable these APIs for the project: "Places API" and "Maps JavaScript API".
#   4. Restrict the key (HTTP referrers) to your domain(s) + localhost before using it
#      anywhere but local development.
#
# Copy this file to ".env" (or ".env.local") in the project root and paste your key below.
# Never commit the real key to version control.
VITE_GOOGLE_MAPS_API_KEY=your_google_maps_api_key_here
